1
00:00:01,838 --> 00:00:03,650
找到他 杀了他
Find him, kill him.

2
00:00:03,684 --> 00:00:06,219
能让他回心转意不是要好得多?
How much better if we were to win him back?

3
00:00:06,253 --> 00:00:08,655
他带着人手穿越荒漠来杀我
He dragged men across the desert to kill me.

4
00:00:08,689 --> 00:00:10,357
大帝已经启程离开了
Our emperor has departed,

5
00:00:10,391 --> 00:00:13,493
但他给耶路撒冷留了一份大礼
but he has left a present for Jerusalem.

6
00:00:13,527 --> 00:00:15,262
大帝的一座雕像
A statue of his likeness.

7
00:00:15,296 --> 00:00:17,797
他要求放在神殿里
Which he commands to be placed in the temple itself.

8
00:00:17,832 --> 00:00:20,867
我们说的可是神殿的毁灭!
This is about the destruction of the temple!

9
00:00:20,902 --> 00:00:24,838
欢迎扫罗成为我们信基督的兄弟
We welcome Saul as our brother in Christ.

10
00:00:24,872 --> 00:00:26,172
你们都疯了
You've all lost your minds.

11
00:00:26,207 --> 00:00:27,807
西门
Simon.

12
00:00:27,842 --> 00:00:29,442
- 这是我的错  - 不要去 扫罗
- This is my fault.  - No, Saul.

13
00:00:29,477 --> 00:00:31,778
我必须要弥补
I have to make it right.

14
00:00:31,813 --> 00:00:33,613
我听说如果你想见某人
I've heard that if you want to meet certain people,

15
00:00:33,648 --> 00:00:34,648
就来这里
then this is the place to come.

16
00:00:34,682 --> 00:00:35,682
罗马的敌人?
Enemies of Rome?

17
00:00:35,716 --> 00:00:38,818
那说吧
So, talk.

18
00:00:38,853 --> 00:00:40,654
- 他在这里  - 找到他
- He's here.  - Find him.

19
00:00:40,688 --> 00:00:42,022
嗷!
Oh!

